1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Sport   | biathlon | volleyball | weightlifting |

