.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, satire, documentary
1. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | satire | documentary |

