.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, aristoff, blend
1. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
2. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5
3. the dannemann-smoker is not to the right of the aristoff-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |     2      |   3   |
| Cigar   | blend | dannemann | aristoff |

 